---
const img = "/brand/ZeroMotion-Layerstyle.png";
import QuantumShowcase from "./QuantumShowcase";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="section-padding reveal"
  aria-labelledby="about-title"
>
  <div
    class="container-page grid md:[grid-template-columns:1.35fr_1fr] gap-8 lg:gap-12 xl:gap-16 items-stretch"
  >
    <div class="relative z-0 md:pr-2 lg:pr-4" aria-hidden="true">
      <div
        class="aspect-[4/5] sm:aspect-[16/10] lg:aspect-[16/9] min-h-[260px] sm:min-h-[320px] lg:min-h-[400px] xl:min-h-[460px]"
      >
        <QuantumShowcase
          client:visible
          className="w-full h-full"
          intensity={1.1}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-center md:pl-6 lg:pl-10 xl:pl-14 max-w-[48ch] ml-auto"
    >
      <h2 id="about-title" class="h2 mb-4">
        Minimalism. Functionality. Precision.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/85 text-lg mb-4">
        We believe Houma, Thibodaux, and every town around us are packed with
        talent, grit, and potential. The only thing missing? A digital presence
        to match it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/85 text-lg mb-4">
        We design clean, timeless brands and high-performance web experiences
        that move with intent — from identity to interface to impression.
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/80">
        This is the moment to step forward. To take the skills, the stories, and
        the hustle of our community and put them where the world can see them.
        We keep the stack lean, the UX elegant, and the speed uncompromised — so
        your brand isn’t just seen, it’s remembered.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
